{"tid":528014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"移植手術時在肝上刻名 英醫生自認：幼稚魯莽","createTime":"2018-01-13T10:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T13:11:34.000Z","uid":110488,"like":225,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4bb7a06d267dd287e333ed76b884821c655d67","tid":528014,"uid":110488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"英國伯明翰伊利沙伯女王醫院一名肝臟移植醫生，涉於2013年為兩名病人移植新肝時，用氬電刀在肝上燒上自己名字的縮寫，到其中一名病人再接受肝臟手術，始被其他醫生揭發。該名醫生承認兩項毆打襲擊罪，判罰款1萬鎊（約10.7萬港元）和12個月社會服務令。 <br />\n<br />\n報道指，53歲醫生布拉姆霍爾（Simon Bramhall）涉嫌用氬電刀，分別於當年2月和8月在兩名病人的新肝上，燒上自己名字簡寫「SB」。其中一名病人於一周後，因新肝未能連接而壞死，另一名醫生在移除壞肝時，驚見肝上有4厘米高的英文字母「SB」，故用手機拍下照片。 <br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後，布拉姆霍爾於翌年辭職，院方強調移植手術成敗與燒字母無關。布拉姆霍爾認罪，自言其所為「幼稚魯莽」。法官宣判時指摘，布拉姆霍爾表現「專業傲慢」，嚴重程度與刑事罪無異。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180113/mobile/bknint-20180113012042198-0113_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180113%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180113012042198-0113_17011_001.html&d=tUDocn2BGiz%2BSbheuNsau%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=23260f8c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180113/mobile/bknint-20180113012042198-0113_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f931839a16edbacac5fc32c2c5208bb068cfcc76","tid":528014,"uid":110488,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5ebb9aab41071ff9f33ba0d13091a1d8e78410","tid":528014,"uid":4525,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:26:41.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"f7746bfe640745bba717224295f9a23e368f317b","tid":528014,"uid":186,"like":178,"dislike":8,"score":170,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"可能個個醫生都會